le IP in firewall allowlist (if any) (~3h)\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\n-*Subtotal: ~39 hours*\\\\\\\\n-\\\\\\\\n-### Sprint 2: Quality Scoring\\\\\\\\n-\\\\\\\\n-**Depends on:** Sprint 0 (Versioning System), Sprint 1 (Quality Scoring)\\\\\\\\n-\\\\\\\\n-- **T-011** [T2] Write operator runbook at `docs/runbooks/generation-backend.md`. (~6h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\n-- **T-012** [T1] End-to-end smoke test on cypherclaw producing one real generated sample audible in a piece. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\n-\\\\\\\\n-*Subtotal: ~9 hours*\\\\\\\\n-\\\\\\\\n-### Sprint 3: Improvement Engine Hardening\\\\\\\\n-\\\\\\\\n-**Depends on:** Sprint 0 (Versioning System), Sprint 2 (Improvement Engine Hardening)\\\\\\\\n-\\\\\\\\n-- **T-013** [T1] Implement `_post_song_generation_hook(score, learning, mood, mode, clap_centroid)` in `tools/duet_composer.py`. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\n-- **T-014** [T1] Implement `_should_queue_now(mode, mood, learning)` heuristic based on cycle rate and homogeneity flags. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\n-- **T-015** [T1] Add systemd unit `cypherclaw-generation-worker.service` running the queue worker. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\n-- **T-016** [T1] Implement `tools/generation_worker.py` as the standalone async worker entry point. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\n-- **T-017** [T1] Implement `/tmp/generation_status.json` diagnostic file written every 30 s by the worker. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\n-- **T-018** [T2] Wire generation status into `operator_diagnostics.py` so the face/inkplate display can show \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"♫ generating\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" / \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"♫ queued: N\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\". (~6h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\n-- **T-019** [T1] Extend `usage_journal.jsonl` to tag each played sample by source. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\n-- **T-020** [T1] Add `generated_content_dominance` antipattern detector to `render/antipatterns.py`. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\n-- **T-021** [T1] Implement self-distance prior on `GenerationConditioner` rejecting requests too similar to recent g