obal_energy/restraint/brightness) in operator diagnostics, never raw one-to-one mappings. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-034 | Build the metric battery: IOI CoV, velocity σ, DNVR/DNODR, pitch-class entropy H1, Grooving Similarity (GS), tempo autocorrelation ρ₁, LZ76 compression ratio, novelty peaks per phrase, silence-at-phrase-boundaries. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-035 | Build anti-pattern tests: quantization ghosting, dynamic compression, motif ossification, random-as-expression (Ljung-Box), symmetric-arc uncanny, dead-silence failure. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-036 | Implement performance-worm logger: 2D trajectory in tempo–loudness space + convex-hull area computation as CI artifact. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-037 | Integrate metric battery + anti-pattern detectors into CI gate with fail-on-regression policy. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-038 | Build audio-rendered SSM + Foote novelty cross-check via librosa on the actual rendered audio. | SHOULD | T2 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-039 | Embed rule-stack provenance in exported audio metadata (e.g., WAV iXML chunk or sidecar JSON) for listener-review workflow. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-040 | Establish listener-review workflow: weekly rendered pieces tagged with rule-stack provenance, ablation tooling documented for operators, review log template in place. | SHOULD | T2 |  |\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ No newline at end of file\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ndiff --git a/sdp/run-log.md b/sdp/run-log.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nindex e10959b..082b4b0 100644\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n--- a/sdp/run-log.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+++ b/sdp/run-log.md\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n@@ -56,3 +56,19 @@\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n | run-t-008@202604